1573
01:46:12,875 --> 01:46:15,041
Shella!

1574
01:46:15,541 --> 01:46:17,375
Shella, come on!

1575
01:46:17,458 --> 01:46:18,583
Oh no, Dide.

1576
01:46:18,666 --> 01:46:20,416
Come on. Let's race!

1577
01:46:22,291 --> 01:46:24,083
Come on. Let's race!

1578
